# Key Equations / Formulas

| Formula | Meaning |
|---|---|
| $Y_t = T_t + S_t + R_t$ | Additive decomposition |
| $Y_t = T_t \times S_t \times R_t$ | Multiplicative decomposition |
| $S_t = Y_t - T_t$ | Seasonal component (additive) |
| $S_t = Y_t / T_t$ | Seasonal component (multiplicative) |

